{"tid":1690316,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[核彈] 恆基、政府利益輸送　錦田過渡性房屋起四層　丁屋僭建即時解決","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:56:17.000Z","uid":39092,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4ddc2c8b294588d0a182cc138cc45d7ca109faea","tid":1690316,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/393574/%E6%81%92%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%80%9F43%E8%90%AC%E5%91%8E%E9%8C%A6%E7%94%B0%E5%9C%B0-3%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%BB%BA2000%E4%BC%99%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E6%80%A7%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F393574%2F%25E6%2581%2592%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2580%259F43%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2591%258E%25E9%258C%25A6%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%259C%25B0-3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25BB%25BA2000%25E4%25BC%2599%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=00ed0c07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/393574/%E6%81%92%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%80%9F43%E8%90%AC%E5%91%8E%E9%8C%A6%E7%94%B0%E5%9C%B0-3%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E5%BB%BA2000%E4%BC%99%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E6%80%A7%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在新一份《施政報告》提出，希望在三年內興建一萬個過渡性房屋。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆在今日（2日）舉辦「同行・共創過渡性房屋」研討會上指出，預計未來可提供6,000伙單位。<br />\n<br />\n恒基地產在會上介紹，他們將展開「同行・共創計劃」，借出鄰近錦上路站的土地，為期七年，以建社會最大社會房屋項目，共提供約2,000伙單位，項目面積共42.8萬平方呎。<br />\n<br />\n樓高四層 用預製組件興建<br />\n<br />\n恒基在會上分享興建「過渡性房屋村」願景。執行董事黃浩明說，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">按初步構思，擬議的過渡性房屋的每棟樓高四層，由預製組件構築而成，單位面積由150至350平方呎不等，切合一至五人家庭，部份更能供長者及傷健人士入住。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黃浩明說，居民步行15分鐘已到錦上路地鐵站，附近有市集、街市及熟食中心。他承認，附近仍有不少棕地，選址並非「完美」的地方，但認為能為居民提供舒適環境。他又指，恒基未來不會「落手」參與營運。<br />\n<br />\n點解係350呎? 因為丁屋只可以起350呎<br />\n但丁屋只可建3層，即係話7年後呢堆樓係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">合法僭建</span></span><br />\n等於送左一層樓比原居民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%8B%E5%AE%87%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25AE%2587%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=41db6a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E5%B1%8B%E5%AE%87%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"556c5c81fecd440885fbacc99c7699846b2bb2e2","tid":1690316,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!"},{"pid":"464745f115d8a29393c2a33a2dd2aecbc4f4c0e9","tid":1690316,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942c16e44c863ee959d47fe6121bffaacc723ee7","tid":1690316,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"618b2df35eae07caa8c59d74e3524c938b1264b7","tid":1690316,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"呢單野好撚大鑊 推呀"},{"pid":"f913d0199af8b3047289587b0eca44e6ddf5c4f4","tid":1690316,"uid":271369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT